		<value condition="Substring(Container.FolderPath,videodb://1/2/,Left) | Substring(Container.FolderPath,videodb://2/2/,Left) | Substring(Container.FolderPath,videodb://3/2/,Left)">[UPPERCASE]$LOCALIZE[369][/UPPERCASE] </value> <!-- title -->
